**#Task 3.4: Color Scheme**

*My color system  created using CSS custom properties.*


/* =========================
   COLOR SYSTEM
========================= */
:root {
    /* Main Colors */
    --color-primary: #2563eb;       /* Blue */
    --color-secondary: #f59e0b;     /* Orange */
    --color-background: #f8fafc;    /* Light Gray */
    --color-text: #1e293b;          /* Dark Gray */
    --color-muted: #64748b;         /* Medium Gray */

    /* Variations */
    --color-primary-light: #60a5fa;
    --color-primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
}

/* =========================
   BASE STYLES
========================= */
body {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 20px;
}

/* =========================
   HEADINGS
========================= */
h1 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
}

h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    font-size: 2rem;
}

h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
}

h4, h5, h6 {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
}

/* =========================
   PARAGRAPHS
========================= */
p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

/* =========================
   LINKS
========================= */
a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

a:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-decoration: underline;
}

/* =========================
   BUTTONS
========================= */
button {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-dark);
}

/* =========================
   HEADER
========================= */
header {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

/* =========================
   FOOTER
========================= */
footer {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

/* =========================
   CARDS / SECTIONS
========================= */
section {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 15px 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

/* =========================
   MUTED TEXT
========================= */
.muted {
    color: var(--color-muted);
}




